{"tid":135041,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果硬屎係一首metal music，軟屎就係一場classical music","createTime":"2017-02-26T04:50:30.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-26T05:20:04.000Z","uid":18827,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de03d82f155c46a08075eed4c025bc9fdc1cf3a5","tid":135041,"uid":18827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T04:50:30.000Z","msg":"如果硬屎係一首metal music，軟屎就係一場classical music。<br />\n<br />\n個種溫柔，個種輕快。<br />\n輕輕用力，連弓、mp、泛音。<br />\n<br />\n噗咚。<br />\n清脆嘅落水聲，係每一個小節嘅完結。<br />\n<br />\n如果用力嘅過程等於琴手嘅演奏，中間嘅每一個屁，就係每一下嘅Pizzicato。<br />\n<br />\n演奏結束，廁所水傳來熱烈嘅拍掌聲。<br />\nE flat？不，拉嘅係G Major<br />\n係韓德爾嘅No.1,in G Major II.Allergro。"},{"pid":"8e85abaedd5c21831f110a8761c5b0fa997a125e","tid":135041,"uid":27064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T04:59:32.000Z","msg":"咁爛屎呢？"},{"pid":"fc6d4197ca1cc6607e5295f8adbfa79f84557992","tid":135041,"uid":18827,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T05:07:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁爛屎呢？</blockquote><br />\n倒帶緊嘅錄音帶"},{"pid":"faf0c73d015abfacb67461e47874062bfba7bf6d","tid":135041,"uid":7344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-26T05:20:04.000Z","msg":"Kpop係爛屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}